name: Leak bucket Multiphos 20 kg
description: Leak bucket Multiphos 20 kg is a mineral feed as a licking compound for cattle during the breeding season and for rations low in phosphorus. Is very well received. For rations with a balanced Ca:P ratio (1.8:1). The Classic licking compound provides the animals with additional minerals, vitamins and trace elements. Ideal for suckler cows. The basic equipment for every pasture. Economical, strong, weatherproof. Without molasses = 100% minerals, does not attract flies. Product is swiss made.
